title: 11-year-old boy wounded after shooting himself in Milwaukee
content:
An 11-year-old boy suffered a self-inflicted gunshot wound early Thursday morning on Milwaukee's north side, police said.
The shooting occurred in the 3600 block of N. 12th St. just before 7:30 a.m., and the child was taken to a hospital. His injuries do not appear to be life-threatening, Milwaukee police said.
No arrests have been made at this time and Milwaukee police continue to investigate.
